&lt;div class="hx:mt-6 hx:leading-7 hx:first:mt-0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;An example linter can be found at &lt;a href="https://github.com/golangci/example-plugin-module-linter"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
