&lt;h2&gt;The Automatic Way&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="the-automatic-way"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#the-automatic-way" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define your building configuration into &lt;code&gt;.custom-gcl.yml&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run the command &lt;code&gt;golangci-lint custom&lt;/code&gt; (or &lt;code&gt;golangci-lint custom -v&lt;/code&gt; to have logs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the plugin inside the &lt;code&gt;linters.settings.custom&lt;/code&gt; section with the type &lt;code&gt;module&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run the resulting custom binary of golangci-lint (&lt;code&gt;./custom-gcl&lt;/code&gt; by default).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Requirements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;git&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Configuration Example&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="configuration-example"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#configuration-example" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
